text":"有的是偷偷摸摸的黄鼠精，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"20391f1f81","type":"paragraph","text":"有的是藏在阴沟里咬人的地头蛇，。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"4ccac5acf2","type":"paragraph","text":"还有的","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"21ae202188","type":"paragraph","text":"是散布无名肿毒的蝎虫精，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"4e78a1ff1f","type":"paragraph","text":"他们欺人、压人、哄人、捧人、监视人、诬陷人","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"3c8860d206","type":"paragraph","text":"甚至要提刀","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"385b9a6b8b","type":"paragraph","text":"杀害“老百姓”！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"37a77448cd","type":"paragraph","text":"请问：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"305a7b83e2","type":"paragraph","text":"是谁在挖沟筑墙？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"7a187a060f","type":"paragraph","text":"是谁在破坏团结？","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"c1b08acd8e","type":"paragraph","text":"是谁在阻碍社会主义前进？","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"979d6dba05","type":"paragraph","text":"是他们！","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"8728946a0f","type":"paragraph","text":"是他们！","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"c32f5508ca","type":"subtitle","text":"风云人物志","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"4fb9a04778","type":"paragraph","text":"姓名    性别  政治成分  职务","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"806d19ff7b","type":"paragraph","text":"方章    男    党员      院长","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"7b3f25eeaa","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：脱离群众，不关心学生，外表朴素，内里奢华，严重的官僚主义者。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"2927d7277e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘御     男    党员      党委书记","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"4634654119","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：游手好闲，吃饭不管事，对鸣不负责任，有严重的官僚主义和宗派主义。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"298573136d","type":"paragraph","text":"吕世华   男    党员      团委书记","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"d93a65ba74","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：操纵党团支部学生会的选举，指名通过，硬说政治部领导司令部，别人反对他便说人家有政治问题，指使自己的亲信后补党员，作青年委员","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"2d13f855b9","type":"paragraph","text":"李志宏    男     党员      工会副主席","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"a6f8b17d2b","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：夫妇每月一百七十元余还要申请补助，他的爱人连化学符号也不识，随夫贵妇拉来作实验员。（同人意见要求追还所骗取的所谓补助费）。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"35f3c743e5","type":"paragraph","text":"李庆元    男     党员      化学系前任秘书","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"0bf57520b8","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：飞扬跋扈，一手遮天，滥用职权，偷换别人名字去福建进修，欺骗党组织，拉×××入党（同人意见要抓回这个无耻的坏蛋作严厉查办）。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"2c17100797","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文俐    女     党员      二中学生","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"ea902a4775","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：在班上作威作福，靠党吃饭，故有女皇之称。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"de15f045b7","type":"paragraph","text":"孙德森    男     党员      史专二学生","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"17d27376be","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：周总理报告时派人监视同学，用组织的压力和各种卑劣手段叫群众通过他当班主席，用党员招牌引诱女同学。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"eb9af81320","type":"paragraph","text":"陈鼎全    男     团员      中一学生","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"0ea8e9cb3d","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：在鸣放中竟持刀杀人，同学意见，要求对这个凶手坏蛋依法处理。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"58aced8a8b","type":"paragraph","text":"彭作祯    男     团员      中专一学生","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"7d26086251","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：一、为人奸滑，外号黑衣使者。二、平时监视群众，有人唱马路天使歌曲他便暗中记名开黑名单。三、在学习人民内部矛盾中压制别人发言，同人意见希大家警惕！！！","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"f3aedbadff","type":"paragraph","text":"徐昆      男     团员      史一学生","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"e489ae3745","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：利用团委委员职权与有爱人的某女同学勾勾搭搭故外号“好色之徒”此人劣迹尚多，民主墙报上遍处皆是。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"35b93ae50f","type":"paragraph","text":"夏先德    男     团员      中专一     团副支书","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"57c89672b2","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：宗派主义偷偷摸摸的约团干部班干部去舐党支部的屁股（指去年），欢送苏加诺老先生和欢迎伏老，私自指派其爪牙去压制民主不让放又说：同学内容稿件正确，又不登出，他说怕人攻击，简直是小脚女人。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"04d1ec7758","type":"paragraph","text":"孙振国    男     团员","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"8d4f9fe65b","type":"paragraph","text":"主要事迹：","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"0cdbeb755d","type":"paragraph","text":"1、乱搞男女关系，见女同学就追，在实习中追一小同学，故曰“采花大盗”","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"efe0739fef","type":"paragraph","text":"2、无耻地骗取助学金，在小组估逼着同学评给他。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"c4383d8398","type":"paragraph","text":"我们从民主墙上摘下他们的事迹，编排出来供大家参考，看该如何治病？但因同人能力有限，搜集不全，希望大家共同协助完成，将你们熟悉的“风云”人物写在后面，以引起病者注意，好找“马列”医生。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"},{"id":"7791ebd9b5","type":"paragraph","text":" 同人识1957.7.8","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230"}],"page":{"id":"3c6aba4828","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5cdaf25230","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}